title: Remove unused dependency on EMF Query
body:
[EMF Query](https://github.com/eclipse-emfservices/emf-query) has been unmaintained for a while. I'd like to drop it [from the SimRel](https://github.com/eclipse-simrel/simrel.build/blob/main/emf-services.aggrcon#L3) but EMF Parsley still depends on it.

AFAICT, it's not actually *used* anywhere, but it is referenced in the target platforms and Oomph setup, and `org.eclipse.emf.parsley.cdo.common` declares an (unused) dependency on it.
